# FIX: Costume Details Not Loading
## Problem The costume detail screen shows: - ❌ Empty image - ❌ Price: 0,00 / jour - ❌ Non Disponible (Not Available) - ❌ No description - ❌ No sizes
## Root Cause The backend database needs to be properly seeded with complete data including: - Brand field - Featured image URL - Proper image relationships - Size relationships
## SOLUTION: Update Backend Seeder
### Step 1: Stop the Backend ```bash # Press Ctrl+C if backend is running ```
### Step 2: Update the Costume Seeder
Replace the content of `backend/database/seeders/CostumeSeeder.php`:
```php <?php
namespace Database\Seeders;
use App\Models\Costume; use App\Models\CostumeImage; use App\Models\Size; use Illuminate\Database\Seeder; use Illuminate\Support\Str;
class CostumeSeeder extends Seeder { public function run(): void { // Clear existing data Costume::query()->delete(); CostumeImage::query()->delete(); Size::query()->delete();
